{"tid":1750521,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想再食屋企飯","createTime":"2019-11-24T12:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T10:43:21.000Z","uid":158899,"like":105,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4270151525a9ad7b5c61c2b6f0c5f7080e8eb6","tid":1750521,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"話說我中午都會係屋企食 但又餐餐臘腸臘肉臘鴨+碟菜<br />\n+上晚隔夜餸（有時冇）<br />\n食撚到我死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係7日有一日係屋企食晚飯先叫做食番啲新鮮餸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係咪出去食算 ？為左自己健康啲食好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家屋係傳統藍絲<br />\n365日入面<br />\n365日都煮飯唔撚出去食 除咗招呼朋友親戚另計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出去食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不孝子"},{"pid":"0ed0bf434ff2841e2dc2ba30522af3aa50cedb1b","tid":1750521,"uid":222907,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:18:09.000Z","msg":"私了佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd008f8ad0db9f438de793f1ab63501b0cf293ab","tid":1750521,"uid":255911,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"唔計政治因素，好好珍惜有屋企飯食。"},{"pid":"a58283eba94eef764368219ea75d94b402b82202","tid":1750521,"uid":158899,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"cd008f8ad0db9f438de793f1ab63501b0cf293ab","tid":1750521,"uid":255911,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:18:39.000Z","msg":"唔計政治因素，好好珍惜有屋企飯食。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:20:10.000Z","msg":"日日臘鴨臘肉臘腸午餐肉豆豉鯪魚<br />\n加埋碟新鮮生菜或者菜心<br />\n<br />\n你食足一個星期7日 中午 食365日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig